I have been following the @hookycookies IG account for a few weeks now drooling over all the posts talking about how amazing her cookies 🍪 are. Well, I finally got the chance to pre-order last week. Sure, I had to drive 30 minutes to go pick them up, but let me tell you...it was SO. WORTH. IT. 😋 She has so many awesome flavors. Pictured here are the ever so popular Crème Brûlée and UbeyBae Cheesecake along with the Churro Caramel and the new Cookie Butter n Cream. So, give her a follow, find an event she'll be at, or go to her website and put in an order. You will not be disappointed!

Taking it easy today. 🖤🍵🤍
Instead of going home after my 2nd dental appointment this week - yes, it's only Wednesday, I decided to head out for some alone time. And I'm glad I did. Getting away recharges me. I find energy and joy in solitude. It makes me a better human. And I think it's good to know what makes you feel better and do better not just for yourself but for and towards others. 

.
